Dialogue: 2,0:21:13.37,0:21:17.21,NozakiED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}không hề ghét đâu
Dialogue: 2,0:21:13.37,0:21:17.21,NozakiED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fs49.5\bord3.375}sono sara ni hantai no
Dialogue: 2,0:21:17.21,0:21:20.67,NozakiED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Đó là cảm xúc em muốn cho anh hay
Dialogue: 2,0:21:17.21,0:21:20.67,NozakiED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fs49.5\bord3.375}kimochi wo tsutaeru no
Dialogue: 2,0:21:20.67,0:21:23.72,NozakiED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}nhưng thật khó nói ra
Dialogue: 2,0:21:20.67,0:21:23.72,NozakiED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fs49.5\bord3.375}tte nandaka muzukashii
Dialogue: 2,0:21:23.72,0:21:28.01,NozakiED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Em chỉ muốn biết cái ý định thật sự thật sự thật sự thật sự
Dialogue: 2,0:21:23.72,0:21:28.01,NozakiED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fs49.5\bord3.375}kimi no hontou no hontou no hontou no hontou no
Dialogue: 2,0:21:28.01,0:21:31.97,NozakiED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}không thể nào giấu giếm đó của anh
Dialogue: 2,0:21:28.01,0:21:31.97,NozakiED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fs49.5\bord3.375}tsutsumikakusanai honne wo
